headline: HQY Expands Access With GLP-1 Telehealth & Direct HSA Platforms
summary: HealthEquity rolls out GLP-1 telehealth and direct HSA enrollment platforms, targeting affordability and growth amid rising healthcare costs and regulatory expansion.
